Tortoise Index Solutions Announces Index Updates for Second Quarter 2016

LEAWOOD, Kan.-- June 10, 2016 (BUSINESS WIRE)--Tortoise Index Solutions today announced upcoming additions and 
      deletions to its indices as part of their regular quarterly rebalancing 
      for the second quarter of 2016, as follows. Following the close of 
      trading on June 17, 2016, the indices will be rebalanced and as a 
      result, the following changes will become effective.
    


           
        



